Title: Sweet, Threatening SHouts
Description: July 25
---
Throw away all your begging bowls at God’s door,
for I have heard the Beloved prefers sweet, threatening shouts, something
on the order of, “Hey, Beloved, my soul is a raging volcano of love for you!
You better start kissing me -- or else!"
